[BORN2BEROOT - Notes]

â€œBorn2BeRoot is a system administration project where I created a Debian server inside a virtual machine. I configured users, groups, and sudo to manage administrator privileges securely. I secured the system by configuring SSH on a custom port, disabling root login, and enabling a firewall with UFW. I applied password policies using PAM to enforce strong passwords. I created a monitoring script that displays system information and scheduled it with cron. Finally, I generated a signature file to prove the integrity of my virtual machine.â€

